sources.sass/_settings.sass:
*
  box-sizing: border-box

body
  font-family: 'Mulish' , sans-serif
  color: $text-color
  background-color: $secondary

.container 
  max-width: 1110px
  margin: auto

img
  max-width: 100%
sources.sass/blocks/_header.sass:
.navbar
  background-color: #fff
  &-top
    display: flex
    align-items: center
    justify-content: space-between
    padding-top: 40px
    padding-bottom: 40px
    &__menu-button
      display: none
  &__search
    margin-right: auto
    margin-left: 108px
  &-bottom
    background-color: $dark
  &-menu
    list-style: none
    margin: 0
    padding: 31px 0
    display: flex
    align-items: center
    justify-content: space-between
    color: $light

    &__link
      color: inherit
      text-decoration: none
      text-transform: uppercase
      font-size: 14px
      line-height: 18px
      
.logo
  width: 177px
.search
  display: flex
  position: relative
  overflow: hidden
  height: 40px
  border-radius: 6px
  &__input
    width: 350px
    height: 100%
    padding-left: 23px
    background-color: #F5FAFE
    border: none
    font-size: 12px
    line-height: 14px
    color: $text-color
    padding-right: 75px

  &__button
    position: absolute
    top: 0
    right: 0
    width: 65px
    height: 100%
    border: none
    background-color: $primary

.user
  display: flex
  align-items: center
  text-decoration: none
  &__avatar
    width: 40px
    height: 40px
    border-radius: 50%
    object-fit: cover
  &__name
    margin-left: 18px
    font-size: 14px
    line-height: 14px
    color: $text-color
sources.sass/blocks/_breadcrumb.sass:
.breadcrumb
  &-list
    display: flex
    align-items: center
    padding: 18px 0px
    margin: 0
    list-style: none
    &__item
      font-size: 10px
      line-height: 13px
      &:not(:last-child)
        &::after
          content: '/'
          margin-right: 4px
    &__link
      text-decoration: none
      color: inherit
sources.sass/blocks/_hotel.sass:
.hotel
  padding-top: 23px
  padding-bottom: 70px
  &-info
    display: flex
    align-items: center
    justify-content: space-between
    &__offer
      margin-left: 14px
      margin-top: 4px
    &__name
      margin-top: 4px
      margin-bottom: 0px
    &__description
      margin: 5px 0
  &-name
    font-size: 24px
    line-height: 30px

  &-wrapper
    display: flex
    flex-wrap: wrap
    align-items: center
  &-description
    font-size: 12px
    line-height: 15px


.stars
  flex-basis: 100%
.offer
  font-size: 10px
  line-height: 13px
  padding: 4px 9px
  background-color: $primary
  border-radius: 3px
  color: $light

.rating
  max-width: 65px
  min-height: 45px
  text-align: center
  color: $light
  background-color: $primary
  border-radius: 4px
  &__text
    font-size: 8px
    line-height: 10px
  &__counter
    font-size: 14px
    line-height: 18px
sources.sass/_media.sass:
@media (max-width: 1200px) 
  .container
    max-width: 960px

@media ( max-width: 992px)
  .container
    max-width: 700px
  .logo
    width: 132px
  .navbar
    &-top
      padding-top: 30px
      padding-bottom: 30px
    &__search
      margin-left: auto
    &-menu
      padding-top: 22px
      padding-bottom: 22px
      &__link
        font-size: 12px
        line-height: 15px
  .search
    &__input
      width: 340px

@media ( max-width: 768px)
  .container
    max-width: 576px
    width: 92%
  .navbar
    &__search, &-menu, &__user
      display: none
  .menu
    &-button
      display: flex
      width: 16px
      height: 11px
      padding: 0
      align-items: center
      justify-content: space-between
      flex-direction: column
      border: none
      background-color: $light
      cursor: pointer
      &__line
        width: 16px
        height: 1px
        background-color: $text-color
  .stars 
    flex-basis: auto
  .hotel
    padding-top: 5px
    &-name
      flex-basis: 100%
    &-wrapper
      justify-content: space-between
    &-info
      &__text
        width: 100%
      &__name
        margin-top: 10px
        margin-bottom: 0
      &__rating
        display: none
      &__offer
        order: -1
        margin-left: 0px
